# This folder holds all driver/installer manifest files for DriverDex.
#
# Files written here by the LDC Builder / AutoSync tools:
#   <Category>.manifest.json            e.g. Audio.manifest.json, Network.manifest.json
#   <Category>.manifest.2.json          overflow shards (>15 MB)
#   installers.manifest.json            standalone installer packages
#
# The lightweight tracker `ldc_index.json` and the SQLite shards `drivers*.db`
# remain at the repository root. Every consumer (DL.py downloader, the D1 sync
# script, and the search worker) discovers manifests through `ldc_index.json`,
# whose `manifest_shards[].filename` values are repo-relative paths such as
# `manifests/Audio.manifest.json`.
